### Basic usage

```console
$ appjail oci run -Pd \
    -o overwrite=force \
    -o virtualnet=":<random> default" \
    -o nat \
    ghcr.io/appjail-makejails/darkhttpd darkhttpd
```

### Using a host's directory

```console
$ appjail oci run -Pd \
    -o overwrite=force \
    -o virtualnet=":<random> default" \
    -o nat \
    -o fstab="/usr/local/poudriere/data/packages /usr/local/www nullfs ro" \
    ghcr.io/appjail-makejails/darkhttpd darkhttpd
```
